      description : "3.2.5 Ensure broadcast ICMP requests are ignored /etc/sysctl.conf /etc/sysctl.d/*"
      info        : "Setting net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts to 1 will cause the system to ignore all

ICMP echo and timestamp requests to broadcast and multicast addresses.

Rationale:
