    <custom_item>
      system      : "Linux"
      type        : CMD_EXEC
      description : "6.2.7 Ensure all users' home directories exist"
      info        : "If the user's home directory does not exist or is unassigned, the user will be placed in '/' and will not be able to write any files or have local environment variables set."
      solution    : "If any users' home directories do not exist, create them and make sure the respective user owns the directory. Users without an assigned home directory should be removed or assigned a home directory as appropriate."
